He then threatened to kill Bennett, whereupon the latter shot him through the head, and the Coroner's jury justified the act.

The schooner Artie Garwood, which came ashore here yesterday morning, Was completely broken up by the surf on the next high tide, at 8 o'clock last night, and the fragments of the vessel are strewn along the beach for a mile. The cargo of coal is in the breakers, completely out of sight, and will be a total lose.

abstract: Representative Hutchins introduced in the House to-day a bill to amend certain sections of the Revised Statutes relative to banks and banking. abstract: AT  ROME.--The year 1848-9 was memorable as a year of national convulsions--of an upheaval of populations and crash of falling thrones.
